name: CleanBlox.
description:
DM me on Discord if you find a issue or want to make a suggestion eoaga#9499.

Now with more colors!

This theme is meant to be used with dark mode.

Built to work with BTRoblox and Roblox+

https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/btroblox-making-roblox-be/hbkpclpemjeibhioopcebchdmohaieln

https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/roblox%2B/jfbnmfgkohlfclfnplnlenbalpppohkm
additional_info:
You can view the progress i have made a long time ago to the rewrite at https://github.com/eoaga/CleanBlox-Rewrite/blob/master/Userstyle

Update 6.7
I accidentally duplicated everything

Update 6.6
Made the sidebar icons local to prevent them from not showing when the CDN is under heavy use.

Fixed the avatar icons again, there is a line around the icons that is visible but i can't fix it without breaking other things.

Fixed the avatar icons backgrounds being white

Mini update to add support for none of the extensions while I work on a rewrite for the style

Changed the colors of the sidebar text when hovering over them.

Updated for the new icons, i am working on changing hosts to prevent icons not showing up sometimes.

Themed the group, login and settings pages. Made some improvements to other pages.

Attempted to clean up some warnings

Update 2.1:
